        "subject": "LU-4679 llite: clean headers and userspace accesses",
        "message": "LU-4679 llite: clean headers and userspace accesses\n\nIn llite ensure that files are including the headers they use. Add\nstatic qualifiers to functions that are not referenced outside of\ntheir file of definition. Replace ad hoc extern definitions in .c\nfiles with declarations in headers. Add the __user address space\nqualifier where appropriate in ll_{dir,file}_ioctl() and related\nfunctions.\n\nSigned-off-by: John L. Hammond <john.hammond@intel.com>\nChange-Id: I9dd1beccc33873307ac05a5597b2bd955fecf8ba\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
